EerieSoft-RecThis version 0.01
==============================

RecThis is a very simple recorder (or wrongly refered to as Logger). It
is aimed at developers who want a fast debug tool that records messages
to a file descriptor (or STDERR), including variable dumps. It has a 0-conf
attitude with the option to set each default option, which aren't many.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Data::Dumper

